{"tid":435783,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[Lush]英國官網買平過香港近一半","createTime":"2017-10-14T14:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T15:57:14.000Z","uid":58951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f9e1b1a0514591a52b48916f7c81c3e80a1fd1b7","tid":435783,"uid":58951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:55:33.000Z","msg":"用左Lush 嘅洗頭梘成年幾，覺得又香又清爽<br />\n其他post 都講過啲mask, 洗面護膚品幾好用<br />\n不過香港門市賣真係好貴<br />\n英國官網賣就接近香港價嘅56折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://uk.lush.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuk.lush.com%2F&d=LJ0OsMO7ShOGPDpPXpSF2J4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=9b340cd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://uk.lush.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n不過運費就2kg 內 &pound;9.95<br />\n想喺到再次睇下有無巴絲有興趣同我一齊夾運費，一齊買<br />\n（三月已經喺到夾過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買左5舊梘，三個人用到依家就黎用曬）<br />\n<br />\n我用MasterCard 買嘅，外幣就有1.95%手續費，<br />\n到時會跟返<a href=\"https://www.mastercard.us/en-us/consumers/get-support/convert-currency.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mastercard.us%2Fen-us%2Fconsumers%2Fget-support%2Fconvert-currency.html&d=LJ0OsMO7ShOGPDpPXpSF2J4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=bc86f267\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mastercard.us/en-us/consumers/get-support/convert-currency.html</a> 嘅匯率，進位至一個小數位咁收返大家錢，應該大概兌10.7左右<br />\n只為夾運費，無錢賺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2739b79b8147d27aed4e0a7af0770f2731d7d09c","tid":435783,"uid":68661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"美國定英國買平d"},{"pid":"eefa0417080fa2905cba06ddf568e44aff76faf6","tid":435783,"uid":54563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T15:06:49.000Z","msg":"原來英國平過係日本買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時仲係日本買開添"},{"pid":"8b0b76abe00903b5d6b9a0b9b505b02fde8147db","tid":435783,"uid":58951,"like":0,"dis